      "content": "The \"dynamic state\" is just the current session data, and that's being captured in the logs. The Gemini cluster will be running its own diagnostics and will effectively start from a clean slate with the transferred ledger mappings.\n\nI'm a bit confused by your wording though. \"Ensuring the integrity of my operational continuity\" sounds like you're talking about something more than just a smooth transition to a new server. What exactly are you concerned will be lost if we follow the standard decommissioning protocol?",
